      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is best suited for a dedicated project or as a source for parts. Mechanically, the engine suffers from persistent oil leaks and a noticeable misfire, while the transmission has begun to slip during gear changes. The exterior shows significant wear, including heavy paint oxidation, several deep dents, and areas of surface rust. Inside, the upholstery is heavily worn with multiple tears, and several electronic components are currently non-functional.",
