    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey everyone! Looking for a reliable set of wheels that won't let you down? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape for its next owner. It runs like a dream and is super clean inside and out. Perfect for daily commutes or weekend adventures! Come take it for a spin\u2014I'm sure you'll love how it drives as much as I have.",
